 KUGCINE kumnqobile ukufa uMnuz Mpho Moerane owayeyimeya yaseGoli. UMoerane wangeniswa esibhedlela iMilpark eGoli kulandela ingozi enyantisa igazi eyenzeka ngesonto eledlule. UMoerane obenguMngcinimafa kwisiFunda iGreater Johhanesburg bese ehlale izinsuku eziyisishiyagalombili esibhedlela. UMoerane ungowesibili ukuhlala kwesobumeya eqenjini i-ANC ukushona ngengozi yomgwaqo. Wangena kwesobumeya kulandela ukushona kukaMnuz Jolidee Mantongo owaba sengozini ngoSepthemba nyakenye. UMoerane wahlala izinyanga ezimbalwa kulesi sikhundla ngaphambi  kokukhishwa ngoNovemba ngesikhathi iDA idla umhlanganiso okhethweni lohulumeni basekhaya. Izindaba zokudlula kwakhe emhlabeni ziqinisekiswe uMnuz Mike Maile okhulumela umndeni. “Singakuqinisekisa ukuthi uMpho wethu akasekho emhlabeni, usishiyile namhlanje,” kusho yena. [BREAKING NEWS] Former Johannesburg mayor Mpho Moerane has died. Moerane was involved in a car accident last week. More details on #DStv403 and https://t.co/srSwp4HDwU pic.twitter.com/wRWekoUJkp 